pr_body: **Describe the Feature you Added** Designed and Implemented Query Screen **How will your Feature Help?** - Users can ask Queries - Users can answer the Queries - Image can be uploaded in a Query - Like option for the answers (only available for the Author of Query) - Changing of the Tag (Answer, Answered) based on-if the Question has been Answered - Author of Query is able to delete the Query Fixes #18
